<section class="fp-faq-section">
  <div class="fp-faq-inner">
    <p class="fp-faq-eyebrow">Common questions</p>
    <h2 class="fp-faq-title">Probably wondering…</h2>

    <div class="fp-faq-grid">
      <div class="fp-faq-item">
        <div class="fp-faq-q">Is this just corporate gifting with a fancier name?</div>
        <div class="fp-faq-a">No. Corporate gifting is a product — you buy it, it ships, done. A relationship moments program is a strategy. We design the touchpoints across your client lifecycle, source the gifts, personalize them, manage the delivery, and review the program with you quarterly. You end up with a system. Not a to-do list.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-faq-item">
        <div class="fp-faq-q">How is this different from Baskits or Giftagram?</div>
        <div class="fp-faq-a">Baskits and Giftagram think about <em>what</em> to send. We think about <em>when</em> to show up, <em>why</em> it matters to that specific relationship, and how to make it happen consistently across your entire client base. They're product companies. We're a relationship partner.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-faq-item">
        <div class="fp-faq-q">We already spend money on client gifts. Does this replace that?</div>
        <div class="fp-faq-a">Yes — and your budget goes further. We take what's currently ad hoc, reactive spending and turn it into a strategic program with better gifts, better timing, and better outcomes. Most clients find their total spend stays the same or decreases while the impact increases significantly.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-faq-item">
        <div class="fp-faq-q">Do you ship across Canada?</div>
        <div class="fp-faq-a">Yes — coast to coast. We work with Canadian-made, women-owned, and sustainable brands committed to planet-friendly packaging. Every gift is 100% recyclable. No wasteful fillers, no single-use tins.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-faq-item">
        <div class="fp-faq-q">How long does it take to get started?</div>
        <div class="fp-faq-a">Most programs are up and running within 4–6 weeks of signing. That includes your Experience Design session, lifecycle mapping, gift curation, and first delivery. We'll walk you through every step.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fp-faq-item">
        <div class="fp-faq-q">What if we only have a few key relationships right now?</div>
        <div class="fp-faq-a">That's exactly who the Starter program is for. Ten relationships done right is more valuable than fifty done inconsistently. <a href="/pages/programs">See program details →</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .fp-faq-section {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 80px 48px;
  }
  .fp-faq-inner {
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .fp-faq-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: #C0552A;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .fp-faq-title {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1F3323;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .fp-faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .fp-faq-q {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1F3323;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .fp-faq-a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #5C5C5C;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .fp-faq-a a {
    color: #C0552A;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .fp-faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .fp-faq-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
    .fp-faq-title { font-size: 28px; }
  }
</style>

